{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"The night before I was heading for Scotland,"},{"time":3000,"text":"I was invited to host the final"},{"time":6000,"text":"of \"China's Got Talent\" show in Shanghai"},{"time":9000,"text":"with the 80,000 live audience in the stadium."},{"time":13000,"text":"Guess who was the performing guest?"},{"time":16000,"text":"Susan Boyle."},{"time":19000,"text":"And I told her, \"I'm going to Scotland the next day.\""},{"time":23000,"text":"She sang beautifully,"},{"time":25000,"text":"and she even managed to say a few words in Chinese:"},{"time":29000,"text":"送你葱"},{"time":32000,"text":"So it's not like \"hello\" or \"thank you,\""},{"time":34000,"text":"that ordinary stuff."},{"time":36000,"text":"It means \"green onion for free.\""},{"time":38000,"text":"Why did she say that?"},{"time":41000,"text":"Because it was a line"},{"time":44000,"text":"from our Chinese parallel Susan Boyle --"},{"time":47000,"text":"a 50-some year-old woman,"},{"time":49000,"text":"a vegetable vendor in Shanghai,"},{"time":51000,"text":"who loves singing Western opera,"},{"time":54000,"text":"but she didn't understand"},{"time":56000,"text":"any English or French or Italian,"},{"time":58000,"text":"so she managed to fill in the lyrics"},{"time":60000,"text":"with vegetable names in Chinese."},{"time":62000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":64000,"text":"And the last sentence of Nessun Dorma"},{"time":67000,"text":"that she was singing in the stadium"},{"time":69000,"text":"was \"green onion for free.\""},{"time":72000,"text":"So [as] Susan Boyle was saying that,"},{"time":75000,"text":"80,000 live audience sang together."},{"time":78000,"text":"That was hilarious."}]},{"cues":[{"time":81000,"text":"So I guess both Susan Boyle"},{"time":84000,"text":"and this vegetable vendor in Shanghai"},{"time":87000,"text":"belonged to otherness."},{"time":89000,"text":"They were the least expected to be successful"},{"time":91000,"text":"in the business called entertainment,"},{"time":94000,"text":"yet their courage and talent brought them through."},{"time":97000,"text":"And a show and a platform"},{"time":100000,"text":"gave them the stage"},{"time":102000,"text":"to realize their dreams."},{"time":105000,"text":"Well, being different is not that difficult."},{"time":109000,"text":"We are all different"},{"time":111000,"text":"from different perspectives."},{"time":113000,"text":"But I think being different is good,"},{"time":115000,"text":"because you present a different point of view."},{"time":118000,"text":"You may have the chance to make a difference."}]},{"cues":[{"time":121000,"text":"My generation has been very fortunate"},{"time":123000,"text":"to witness and participate"},{"time":125000,"text":"in the historic transformation of China"},{"time":128000,"text":"that has made so many changes"},{"time":130000,"text":"in the past 20, 30 years."},{"time":133000,"text":"I remember that in the year of 1990,"},{"time":136000,"text":"when I was graduating from college,"},{"time":138000,"text":"I was applying for a job in the sales department"},{"time":141000,"text":"of the first five-star hotel in Beijing,"},{"time":143000,"text":"Great Wall Sheraton -- it's still there."},{"time":147000,"text":"So after being interrogated"},{"time":149000,"text":"by this Japanese manager for a half an hour,"},{"time":151000,"text":"he finally said,"},{"time":153000,"text":"\"So, Miss Yang,"},{"time":155000,"text":"do you have any questions to ask me?\""},{"time":158000,"text":"I summoned my courage and poise and said,"},{"time":161000,"text":"\"Yes, but could you let me know,"},{"time":163000,"text":"what actually do you sell?\""},{"time":166000,"text":"I didn't have a clue what a sales department was about"},{"time":168000,"text":"in a five-star hotel."},{"time":170000,"text":"That was the first day I set my foot"},{"time":172000,"text":"in a five-star hotel."}]},{"cues":[{"time":174000,"text":"Around the same time,"},{"time":176000,"text":"I was going through an audition --"},{"time":179000,"text":"the first ever open audition"},{"time":181000,"text":"by national television in China --"},{"time":184000,"text":"with another thousand college girls."},{"time":187000,"text":"The producer told us"},{"time":189000,"text":"they were looking for some sweet, innocent"},{"time":191000,"text":"and beautiful fresh face."},{"time":194000,"text":"So when it was my turn, I stood up and said,"},{"time":197000,"text":"\"Why [do] women's personalities on television"},{"time":200000,"text":"always have to be beautiful, sweet, innocent"},{"time":203000,"text":"and, you know, supportive?"},{"time":206000,"text":"Why can't they have their own ideas"},{"time":208000,"text":"and their own voice?\""},{"time":210000,"text":"I thought I kind of offended them."},{"time":214000,"text":"But actually, they were impressed by my words."},{"time":218000,"text":"And so I was in the second round of competition,"},{"time":220000,"text":"and then the third and the fourth."},{"time":222000,"text":"After seven rounds of competition,"},{"time":224000,"text":"I was the last one to survive it."},{"time":227000,"text":"So I was on a national television prime-time show."},{"time":230000,"text":"And believe it or not,"},{"time":232000,"text":"that was the first show on Chinese television"},{"time":234000,"text":"that allowed its hosts"},{"time":236000,"text":"to speak out of their own minds"},{"time":238000,"text":"without reading an approved script."},{"time":241000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":245000,"text":"And my weekly audience at that time"},{"time":247000,"text":"was between 200 to 300 million people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":251000,"text":"Well after a few years,"},{"time":253000,"text":"I decided to go to the U.S. and Columbia University"},{"time":256000,"text":"to pursue my postgraduate studies,"},{"time":258000,"text":"and then started my own media company,"},{"time":260000,"text":"which was unthought of"},{"time":263000,"text":"during the years that I started my career."},{"time":265000,"text":"So we do a lot of things."},{"time":267000,"text":"I've interviewed more than a thousand people in the past."},{"time":270000,"text":"And sometimes I have young people approaching me"},{"time":273000,"text":"say, \"Lan, you changed my life,\""},{"time":275000,"text":"and I feel proud of that."},{"time":277000,"text":"But then we are also so fortunate"},{"time":279000,"text":"to witness the transformation of the whole country."},{"time":282000,"text":"I was in Beijing's bidding for the Olympic Games."},{"time":286000,"text":"I was representing the Shanghai Expo."},{"time":288000,"text":"I saw China embracing the world"},{"time":290000,"text":"and vice versa."},{"time":292000,"text":"But then sometimes I'm thinking,"},{"time":295000,"text":"what are today's young generation up to?"},{"time":299000,"text":"How are they different,"},{"time":301000,"text":"and what are the differences they are going to make"},{"time":303000,"text":"to shape the future of China,"},{"time":305000,"text":"or at large, the world?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":308000,"text":"So today I want to talk about young people"},{"time":310000,"text":"through the platform of social media."},{"time":313000,"text":"First of all, who are they? [What] do they look like?"},{"time":316000,"text":"Well this is a girl called Guo Meimei --"},{"time":318000,"text":"20 years old, beautiful."},{"time":320000,"text":"She showed off her expensive bags,"},{"time":323000,"text":"clothes and car"},{"time":325000,"text":"on her microblog,"},{"time":327000,"text":"which is the Chinese version of Twitter."},{"time":329000,"text":"And she claimed to be the general manager of Red Cross"},{"time":333000,"text":"at the Chamber of Commerce."},{"time":336000,"text":"She didn't realize"},{"time":338000,"text":"that she stepped on a sensitive nerve"},{"time":340000,"text":"and aroused national questioning,"},{"time":342000,"text":"almost a turmoil,"},{"time":344000,"text":"against the credibility of Red Cross."},{"time":347000,"text":"The controversy was so heated"},{"time":350000,"text":"that the Red Cross had to open a press conference"},{"time":352000,"text":"to clarify it,"},{"time":354000,"text":"and the investigation is going on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":356000,"text":"So far, as of today,"},{"time":359000,"text":"we know that she herself made up that title --"},{"time":362000,"text":"probably because she feels proud to be associated with charity."},{"time":365000,"text":"All those expensive items"},{"time":367000,"text":"were given to her as gifts"},{"time":369000,"text":"by her boyfriend,"},{"time":371000,"text":"who used to be a board member"},{"time":373000,"text":"in a subdivision of Red Cross at Chamber of Commerce."},{"time":376000,"text":"It's very complicated to explain."},{"time":379000,"text":"But anyway, the public still doesn't buy it."},{"time":382000,"text":"It is still boiling."},{"time":384000,"text":"It shows us a general mistrust"},{"time":387000,"text":"of government or government-backed institutions,"},{"time":390000,"text":"which lacked transparency in the past."},{"time":393000,"text":"And also it showed us"},{"time":395000,"text":"the power and the impact of social media"},{"time":398000,"text":"as microblog."}]},{"cues":[{"time":400000,"text":"Microblog boomed in the year of 2010,"},{"time":403000,"text":"with visitors doubled"},{"time":405000,"text":"and time spent on it tripled."},{"time":408000,"text":"Sina.com, a major news portal,"},{"time":410000,"text":"alone has more than 140 million microbloggers."},{"time":414000,"text":"On Tencent, 200 million."},{"time":416000,"text":"The most popular blogger --"},{"time":418000,"text":"it's not me --"},{"time":420000,"text":"it's a movie star,"},{"time":422000,"text":"and she has more than 9.5 million followers, or fans."},{"time":426000,"text":"About 80 percent of those microbloggers are young people,"},{"time":429000,"text":"under 30 years old."},{"time":432000,"text":"And because, as you know,"},{"time":434000,"text":"the traditional media is still heavily controlled by the government,"},{"time":437000,"text":"social media offers an opening"},{"time":439000,"text":"to let the steam out a little bit."},{"time":441000,"text":"But because you don't have many other openings,"},{"time":444000,"text":"the heat coming out of this opening"},{"time":447000,"text":"is sometimes very strong, active"},{"time":450000,"text":"and even violent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":452000,"text":"So through microblogging,"},{"time":454000,"text":"we are able to understand Chinese youth even better."},{"time":457000,"text":"So how are they different?"},{"time":459000,"text":"First of all, most of them were born"},{"time":461000,"text":"in the 80s and 90s,"},{"time":463000,"text":"under the one-child policy."},{"time":466000,"text":"And because of selected abortion"},{"time":468000,"text":"by families who favored boys to girls,"},{"time":470000,"text":"now we have ended up"},{"time":472000,"text":"with 30 million more young men than women."},{"time":475000,"text":"That could pose"},{"time":477000,"text":"a potential danger to the society,"},{"time":479000,"text":"but who knows;"},{"time":481000,"text":"we're in a globalized world,"},{"time":483000,"text":"so they can look for girlfriends from other countries."},{"time":487000,"text":"Most of them have fairly good education."},{"time":490000,"text":"The illiteracy rate in China among this generation"},{"time":493000,"text":"is under one percent."},{"time":496000,"text":"In cities, 80 percent of kids go to college."},{"time":499000,"text":"But they are facing an aging China"},{"time":503000,"text":"with a population above 65 years old"},{"time":506000,"text":"coming up with seven-point-some percent this year,"},{"time":509000,"text":"and about to be 15 percent"},{"time":511000,"text":"by the year of 2030."},{"time":513000,"text":"And you know we have the tradition"},{"time":515000,"text":"that younger generations support the elders financially,"},{"time":517000,"text":"and taking care of them when they're sick."},{"time":519000,"text":"So it means young couples"},{"time":521000,"text":"will have to support four parents"},{"time":524000,"text":"who have a life expectancy of 73 years old."}]},{"cues":[{"time":528000,"text":"So making a living is not that easy"},{"time":530000,"text":"for young people."},{"time":532000,"text":"College graduates are not in short supply."},{"time":535000,"text":"In urban areas,"},{"time":537000,"text":"college graduates find the starting salary"},{"time":539000,"text":"is about 400 U.S. dollars a month,"},{"time":541000,"text":"while the average rent"},{"time":543000,"text":"is above $500."},{"time":545000,"text":"So what do they do? They have to share space --"},{"time":548000,"text":"squeezed in very limited space"},{"time":550000,"text":"to save money --"},{"time":552000,"text":"and they call themselves \"tribe of ants.\""},{"time":555000,"text":"And for those who are ready to get married"},{"time":557000,"text":"and buy their apartment,"},{"time":559000,"text":"they figured out they have to work"},{"time":561000,"text":"for 30 to 40 years"},{"time":563000,"text":"to afford their first apartment."},{"time":565000,"text":"That ratio in America"},{"time":567000,"text":"would only cost a couple five years to earn,"},{"time":569000,"text":"but in China it's 30 to 40 years"},{"time":572000,"text":"with the skyrocketing real estate price."}]},{"cues":[{"time":576000,"text":"Among the 200 million migrant workers,"},{"time":579000,"text":"60 percent of them are young people."},{"time":582000,"text":"They find themselves sort of sandwiched"},{"time":584000,"text":"between the urban areas and the rural areas."},{"time":587000,"text":"Most of them don't want to go back to the countryside,"},{"time":590000,"text":"but they don't have the sense of belonging."},{"time":592000,"text":"They work for longer hours"},{"time":594000,"text":"with less income, less social welfare."},{"time":597000,"text":"And they're more vulnerable"},{"time":599000,"text":"to job losses,"},{"time":601000,"text":"subject to inflation,"},{"time":603000,"text":"tightening loans from banks,"},{"time":605000,"text":"appreciation of the renminbi,"},{"time":607000,"text":"or decline of demand"},{"time":609000,"text":"from Europe or America"},{"time":611000,"text":"for the products they produce."},{"time":613000,"text":"Last year, though,"},{"time":615000,"text":"an appalling incident"},{"time":617000,"text":"in a southern OEM manufacturing compound in China:"},{"time":620000,"text":"13 young workers"},{"time":622000,"text":"in their late teens and early 20s"},{"time":624000,"text":"committed suicide,"},{"time":626000,"text":"just one by one like causing a contagious disease."},{"time":630000,"text":"But they died because of all different personal reasons."},{"time":634000,"text":"But this whole incident"},{"time":636000,"text":"aroused a huge outcry from society"},{"time":638000,"text":"about the isolation,"},{"time":640000,"text":"both physical and mental,"},{"time":642000,"text":"of these migrant workers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":644000,"text":"For those who do return back to the countryside,"},{"time":646000,"text":"they find themselves very welcome locally,"},{"time":649000,"text":"because with the knowledge, skills and networks"},{"time":651000,"text":"they have learned in the cities,"},{"time":653000,"text":"with the assistance of the Internet,"},{"time":655000,"text":"they're able to create more jobs,"},{"time":658000,"text":"upgrade local agriculture and create new business"},{"time":660000,"text":"in the less developed market."},{"time":662000,"text":"So for the past few years, the coastal areas,"},{"time":665000,"text":"they found themselves in a shortage of labor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":668000,"text":"These diagrams show"},{"time":670000,"text":"a more general social background."},{"time":672000,"text":"The first one is the Engels coefficient,"},{"time":675000,"text":"which explains that the cost of daily necessities"},{"time":678000,"text":"has dropped its percentage"},{"time":680000,"text":"all through the past decade,"},{"time":682000,"text":"in terms of family income,"},{"time":684000,"text":"to about 37-some percent."},{"time":687000,"text":"But then in the last two years,"},{"time":689000,"text":"it goes up again to 39 percent,"},{"time":691000,"text":"indicating a rising living cost."},{"time":694000,"text":"The Gini coefficient"},{"time":696000,"text":"has already passed the dangerous line of 0.4."},{"time":699000,"text":"Now it's 0.5 --"},{"time":701000,"text":"even worse than that in America --"},{"time":704000,"text":"showing us the income inequality."},{"time":707000,"text":"And so you see this whole society"},{"time":709000,"text":"getting frustrated"},{"time":711000,"text":"about losing some of its mobility."},{"time":714000,"text":"And also, the bitterness and even resentment"},{"time":717000,"text":"towards the rich and the powerful"},{"time":719000,"text":"is quite widespread."},{"time":721000,"text":"So any accusations of corruption"},{"time":723000,"text":"or backdoor dealings between authorities or business"},{"time":727000,"text":"would arouse a social outcry"},{"time":729000,"text":"or even unrest."}]},{"cues":[{"time":731000,"text":"So through some of the hottest topics on microblogging,"},{"time":735000,"text":"we can see what young people care most about."},{"time":738000,"text":"Social justice and government accountability"},{"time":740000,"text":"runs the first in what they demand."},{"time":743000,"text":"For the past decade or so,"},{"time":745000,"text":"a massive urbanization and development"},{"time":749000,"text":"have let us witness a lot of reports"},{"time":752000,"text":"on the forced demolition"},{"time":754000,"text":"of private property."},{"time":756000,"text":"And it has aroused huge anger and frustration"},{"time":759000,"text":"among our young generation."},{"time":761000,"text":"Sometimes people get killed,"},{"time":763000,"text":"and sometimes people set themselves on fire to protest."},{"time":767000,"text":"So when these incidents are reported"},{"time":769000,"text":"more and more frequently on the Internet,"},{"time":771000,"text":"people cry for the government to take actions to stop this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":774000,"text":"So the good news is that earlier this year,"},{"time":777000,"text":"the state council passed a new regulation"},{"time":780000,"text":"on house requisition and demolition"},{"time":783000,"text":"and passed the right"},{"time":785000,"text":"to order forced demolition from local governments"},{"time":787000,"text":"to the court."},{"time":790000,"text":"Similarly, many other issues concerning public safety"},{"time":793000,"text":"is a hot topic on the Internet."},{"time":796000,"text":"We heard about polluted air,"},{"time":798000,"text":"polluted water, poisoned food."},{"time":801000,"text":"And guess what, we have faked beef."},{"time":804000,"text":"They have sorts of ingredients"},{"time":806000,"text":"that you brush on a piece of chicken or fish,"},{"time":809000,"text":"and it turns it to look like beef."},{"time":812000,"text":"And then lately,"},{"time":814000,"text":"people are very concerned about cooking oil,"},{"time":816000,"text":"because thousands of people have been found"},{"time":819000,"text":"[refining] cooking oil"},{"time":821000,"text":"from restaurant slop."},{"time":823000,"text":"So all these things"},{"time":825000,"text":"have aroused a huge outcry from the Internet."},{"time":829000,"text":"And fortunately,"},{"time":831000,"text":"we have seen the government"},{"time":833000,"text":"responding more timely and also more frequently"},{"time":836000,"text":"to the public concerns."}]},{"cues":[{"time":838000,"text":"While young people seem to be very sure"},{"time":840000,"text":"about their participation"},{"time":842000,"text":"in public policy-making,"},{"time":844000,"text":"but sometimes they're a little bit lost"},{"time":846000,"text":"in terms of what they want for their personal life."},{"time":849000,"text":"China is soon to pass the U.S."},{"time":851000,"text":"as the number one market"},{"time":853000,"text":"for luxury brands --"},{"time":855000,"text":"that's not including the Chinese expenditures"},{"time":857000,"text":"in Europe and elsewhere."},{"time":859000,"text":"But you know what, half of those consumers"},{"time":862000,"text":"are earning a salary below 2,000 U.S. dollars."},{"time":865000,"text":"They're not rich at all."},{"time":867000,"text":"They're taking those bags and clothes"},{"time":870000,"text":"as a sense of identity and social status."},{"time":873000,"text":"And this is a girl explicitly saying"},{"time":875000,"text":"on a TV dating show"},{"time":877000,"text":"that she would rather cry in a BMW"},{"time":879000,"text":"than smile on a bicycle."},{"time":882000,"text":"But of course, we do have young people"},{"time":884000,"text":"who would still prefer to smile,"},{"time":886000,"text":"whether in a BMW or [on] a bicycle."}]},{"cues":[{"time":888000,"text":"So in the next picture, you see a very popular phenomenon"},{"time":892000,"text":"called \"naked\" wedding, or \"naked\" marriage."},{"time":895000,"text":"It does not mean they will wear nothing in the wedding,"},{"time":898000,"text":"but it shows that these young couples are ready to get married"},{"time":901000,"text":"without a house, without a car, without a diamond ring"},{"time":904000,"text":"and without a wedding banquet,"},{"time":906000,"text":"to show their commitment to true love."},{"time":909000,"text":"And also, people are doing good through social media."},{"time":912000,"text":"And the first picture showed us"},{"time":914000,"text":"that a truck caging 500 homeless and kidnapped dogs"},{"time":918000,"text":"for food processing"},{"time":920000,"text":"was spotted and stopped on the highway"},{"time":923000,"text":"with the whole country watching"},{"time":925000,"text":"through microblogging."},{"time":927000,"text":"People were donating money, dog food"},{"time":929000,"text":"and offering volunteer work to stop that truck."},{"time":932000,"text":"And after hours of negotiation,"},{"time":934000,"text":"500 dogs were rescued."},{"time":937000,"text":"And here also people are helping to find missing children."},{"time":941000,"text":"A father posted his son's picture onto the Internet."},{"time":944000,"text":"After thousands of resends in relay,"},{"time":947000,"text":"the child was found,"},{"time":949000,"text":"and we witnessed the reunion of the family"},{"time":952000,"text":"through microblogging."}]},{"cues":[{"time":954000,"text":"So happiness is the most popular word"},{"time":957000,"text":"we have heard through the past two years."},{"time":960000,"text":"Happiness is not only related"},{"time":963000,"text":"to personal experiences and personal values,"},{"time":965000,"text":"but also, it's about the environment."},{"time":967000,"text":"People are thinking about the following questions:"},{"time":970000,"text":"Are we going to sacrifice our environment further"},{"time":973000,"text":"to produce higher GDP?"},{"time":976000,"text":"How are we going to perform our social and political reform"},{"time":979000,"text":"to keep pace with economic growth,"},{"time":982000,"text":"to keep sustainability and stability?"},{"time":985000,"text":"And also, how capable is the system"},{"time":988000,"text":"of self-correctness"},{"time":990000,"text":"to keep more people content"},{"time":993000,"text":"with all sorts of friction going on at the same time?"},{"time":996000,"text":"I guess these are the questions people are going to answer."},{"time":999000,"text":"And our younger generation"},{"time":1001000,"text":"are going to transform this country"},{"time":1003000,"text":"while at the same time being transformed themselves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1007000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1009000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}